OL,6,FSanitiser out, air fryers in: How the
OL,7,F'inflation basket' reflects our
OL,8,Fchanging nation
OL,10,FVinyl records and air fryers have been
OL,11,Fadded to the basket of goods used to
OL,12,Fcalculate while a pub-bought pint of
OL,13,FGuinness and hand sanitiser have been
OL,14,Fremoved.
OL,16,FThe Office for National Statistics
OL,17,F(ONS)'s virtual basket contains more
OL,18,Fthan 700 items that are representative
OL,19,Fof the goods and services that people
OL,20,Ftypically spend money on.
