OL,13,FMore than three decades later, vinyl
OL,14,Fhas become popular again and is added
OL,15,Fto the list for this year, while tapes
OL,16,Fis nowhere to be seen.
OL,18,FAnother addition to the list is a
OL,19,Fresult of the energy crisis.
