OL,6,FAs energy bills soared, , with
OL,7,Fmanufacturers saying they are a lower-
OL,8,Fenergy way of cooking.
OL,10,FThere is a happier sign of the times
OL,11,Fin the removals from the list, as hand
OL,12,Fsanitisers were removed.
OL,14,FHand sanitisers were added to the
OL,15,Fbasket in 2021, to reflect how the
OL,16,FCovid-19 pandemic was changing
OL,17,Fpeoples' shopping habits.
OL,19,FThis year they have been removed.
