OL,6,FSome removals from the list are less
OL,7,Fabout what people are buying, and more
OL,8,Fthat the ONS does not think it needs
OL,9,Fto track the price of that item
OL,10,Fspecifically.
OL,12,FThat is the case for Guinness.
OL,14,FThis year, draught stout has been
OL,15,Fremoved from the list, because the
OL,16,Fprice of draught stout and draught
OL,17,Fbitter often move together, so the ONS
OL,18,Fdoes not think it needs to track both
OL,19,Fof them.
