OL,6,FOther additions to the list this year
OL,7,Finclude, rice cakes, sunflower and
OL,8,Fpumpkin seeds, and women's socks.
OL,10,FPopcorn, loose cooked ham, hot
OL,11,Frotisserie cooked whole chicken, sofa
OL,12,Fbeds were all removed, as pull-out
OL,13,Fbeds become more popular, and bakeware.
OL,15,FONS deputy director for prices, Matt
OL,16,FCorder said the offers "a fascinating
OL,17,Fsnapshot of consumer spending through
OL,18,Fthe years".
