OL,6,FOften the basket reflects the adoption
OL,7,Fof new technology, but the return of
OL,8,Fvinyl records shows how cultural
OL,9,Frevivals can affect our spending.
OL,11,F"We are also seeing the impact of the
OL,12,Fpandemic fading from the basket with
OL,13,Fthe removal of hand sanitiser due to
OL,14,Fdecreased demand," Mr Corder said.
OL,16,F"Healthier lifestyle products continue
OL,17,Fto influence consumer choice reflected
OL,18,Fby the addition of the air fryer,
OL,19,Fspray oils and rice cakes as well as
OL,20,Fsunflower and pumpkin seeds."
